 In order to compile you have to specify the following envirorment variables:
   - CC: C-compiler to use. Use mpicc if you compile with FF_MPI_INIT (enabled by default).
   - P4_INCLUDE_DIR: path to Portals 4 "include" directory
   - P4_LIB_DIR: path to Portals 4 library directory
   - P4_TEST_DIR: path to Portals 4 "test" directory
